# ── Model weights (.pth) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These are excluded from git — files are 89–270 MB each and exceed
# GitHub's 100 MB per-file hard limit.
#
# Checkpoint folder structure (managed manually, upload to Kaggle as datasets):
#
#   Road Training Checkpoints/
#     road_ckpt_ep05.pth   ← periodic checkpoints saved every 5 epochs
#     road_ckpt_ep10.pth   ← contain: model + optimizer + scheduler + history
#     road_ckpt_ep15.pth   ← use RESUME_FROM_CKPT in train_road.py to restore
#     road_ckpt_ep20.pth  …  road_ckpt_ep35.pth
#
#   Best path/
#     road_model_best.pth        ← best val_loss during road training
#     inpainting_best.pth        ← best val hole-loss during inpainting training
#     landcover_best.pth         ← best val mIoU during landcover training
#     building_model_best.pth    ← best val IoU during building detection training
#
*.pth
*.pt
*.ckpt
*.safetensors

# ── Python cache & build artefacts ────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.egg-info/
dist/
build/
.eggs/

